      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Pew Pew",
      "review_description": "Room Invaders is a charmingly chaotic mixed-reality wave-shooter that plops an alien infant named Zooky onto your sofa, then rips open the walls of your actual room to pour in neon-hued abductors. The Quest 3’s full-color passthrough turns coffee tables into cover and hallway doorframes into flanking routes, making each duck, dodge, and laser-blast feel thrillingly physical. Between rounds you cash in on weapon upgrades, grenade launchers, beam rifles, and more that keep the firefights fresh and playful quips prevent the intensity from becoming grim. If you’re hunting for a bite-sized shooter that makes you grin as much as it makes you sweat, Room Invaders is an easy recommendation.",
