      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Remapping issues",
      "review_description": "It doesn’t remap there’s no setting option for it. i even tried uninstalling and reinstalling it back.",
      "date": 1751088588,
      "review_helpful_count": 3,
      "author_display_name": "metro.husani",
      "author_alias": "metro.husani",
      "developer_response": {
        "body": "Sorry you’re running into trouble. We're currently in Early Access and actively hunting down bugs just like this one.\n\nIf the game keeps asking for a new room setup repeatedly, this usually indicates insufficient play space.\n\nSolution:\n1. Make sure you have at least 2m x 2m of clear play space\n2. If the space is too small, try finding a larger room to play in\n\nThe room space data is not stored by the game, if you want to reset it you will need to remove your room data from Meta operative systeam menu",
        "date": 1751142797
      }
